notes: JH Kallis 100 in 177 mins off 129 balls, 11x4
VS Solanki 100 in 130 mins off 101 balls, 16x4

milestones.description: Marcus Trescothick and Solanki's 199-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 193 between Graham Gooch and Bill Athey

stories.title: Solanki lands in the big time
stories.summary:
Vikram Solanki: displays the full charm and range of the great wristy Indian strokeplayers    
 
 
 Vikram Solanki finally arrived as an international batsman with his innings of 106 against South Africa at The Oval
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Ralph Dellor

stories.title: Vaughan set to play next game
stories.summary: Michael Vaughan expects to be fit for England's next triangular series match against Zimbabwe on July 1

stories.title: Hundreds from Solanki and Trescothick sink South Africa
stories.summary:
Man of the Match Vikram Solanki is congratulated by Marcus Trescothick on reaching his maiden England hundred    
 
 
 England wobbled in the final furlong, but superb hundreds from Marcus Trescothick and Vikram Solanki - his first in England colours
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by Martin Williamson
